      • run

        protected double run(double[] weights)
        Description copied from class: Hyperband
        Run and eval on the given weights using the given budget (ratio of max resources) and give back its score (lower is better). This method may modify weights if it wants to store a different set of weights than those initially passed in. The rules have already been set with the given weights, they are only passed in so the method has a chance to modify them before the result is stored. This is a prime method for child classes to override. Implementers should make sure to correct (negate) the value that comes back from the Evaluator if lower is better for that evaluator.
        Overrides:
        run in class Hyperband
